02:37.716 --> 02:39.716
- Oh.
- We understand.

02:40.282 --> 02:44.550
Okay, Batch Boys,
the festivities official begin now.

02:44.575 --> 02:46.408
Let's just grab a couple cabs or...

02:46.435 --> 02:49.002
Oh, my God. What do we have here?

02:49.027 --> 02:50.113
- Damn!
- [HORN HONKS]

02:50.138 --> 02:52.040
- Nice work on the limo, Charles.
- [TIRES SCREECH]

02:52.064 --> 02:53.110
