that actually gets you drunk.

03:47.525 --> 03:49.259
I love you, dude,
but you haven't had the craziest life.

03:49.283 --> 03:51.183
- That's not true.
- I've done stuff.

03:51.459 --> 03:53.482
Just say ones that are
a little less wild.

03:53.507 --> 03:56.146
