amount of conditioner.

04:19.284 --> 04:21.813
- They make the conditioner.
- They know what they're doing.

04:21.838 --> 04:23.427
- This is lame.
- Let's play something else.

04:23.451 --> 04:24.990
No. No-no-no, okay.

04:25.026 --> 04:26.534
Never have I ever

04:26.559 --> 04:29.277
had a one-night stand
with a guy from a band.

04:29.324 --> 04:30.996
Whoops! Yes, I have!

04:31.032 --> 04:34.466
- Whoa, I am V impressed, Amy.
- V impressed.

04:34.535 --> 04:35.830
In fact, Kylie,

04:35.855 --> 04:37.636
it was the lead singer
of your wedding band.

04:37.671 --> 04:38.971
Boom! That's right.

04:39.006 --> 04:40.539
I'm a wild girl!

04:40.574 --> 04:42.141
Watch out, Madonna. [LAUGHS]

04:42.176 --> 04:45.213
Uh, Ames? I told Jake that
you really liked that band

04:45.258 --> 04:47.391
