wedding as a surprise.

04:47.615 --> 04:49.014
What?

04:49.050 --> 04:50.718
[SOFTLY] Surprise!

04:51.484 --> 04:53.819
So, according to this map,

04:53.854 --> 04:56.505
the restaurant should be right here.

04:56.619 --> 04:58.419
But it's just an old abandoned building.

04:58.444 --> 05:00.294
- That's odd.
- Unless...

05:00.728 --> 05:03.169
You don't think when the sun sets that

05:03.194 --> 05:06.131
certain letters on that graffiti
wall will be illuminated

05:06.167 --> 05:07.633
by a shaft of light?

05:07.668 --> 05:10.073
I don't think that.
We've been at this bachelor party

05:10.110 --> 05:12.580
for over an hour, wandering
around aimlessly

05:12.606 --> 05:14.973
and we haven't done one
bachelor party thing!

05:15.009 --> 05:17.609
Well, Terry, if you'd like,
I could share a lewd story.

05:17.645 --> 05:19.478
Kevin got me quite horny this morning.

05:19.513 --> 05:20.612
[LAUGHS] Oh, see?

05:20.648 --> 05:22.714
- Come on, guys.
- I'm hungry!

05:22.750 --> 05:24.404
Oh, you're in luck; the fanny pack

05:24.429 --> 05:25.771
is filled with granola.

05:26.294 --> 05:29.411
Mmm! Loose granola.

05:29.505 --> 05:31.690
I don't want fanny granola!

05:31.725 --> 05:33.469
I want steaks and whiskey!

05:33.494 --> 05:35.157
Is this whole night
just gonna be puzzles?

05:35.182 --> 05:37.015
- Good question.
- Perhaps that's something

05:37.040 --> 05:38.774
- the limo can answer!
- [TIRES SCREECH]

05:38.799 --> 05:40.165
- Oh.
- Oh, yes, the limo's back!

05:40.201 --> 05:41.824
We finally get to ride in the limo.

05:41.849 --> 05:43.613
Nope. The limo is not for us.
This is something else.

05:43.637 --> 05:45.037
Oh, no, I'm being kidnapped!

05:45.072 --> 05:48.807
We have your friend!
Your mission is to find him!

05:48.843 --> 05:50.320
Is that a Serbian accent?

05:50.345 --> 05:51.677
It is. Write that down for later.

05:51.712 --> 05:53.445
Oh! I'll see you in six hours.

05:53.481 --> 05:54.713
Six hours?

05:54.748 --> 05:57.116
Joe, let us get in the limo, please!

05:57.151 --> 05:58.884
Terry's so hungry!

05:59.114 --> 06:00.756
No!

06:04.349 --> 06:06.459
Okay, let's not get
discouraged just because...

06:06.484 --> 06:08.193
We've been doing this for 93 minutes

06:08.218 --> 06:09.985
and we haven't figured
out one damn clue.

06:10.020 --> 06:11.753
That's why I said to
not get discouraged.

06:11.789 --> 06:14.089
All right, what about book two?
Maybe it's a code.

06:14.124 --> 06:15.529
All we have to do is decipher

06:15.554 --> 06:17.169
this list of thousands
of random numbers.

06:17.201 --> 06:19.795
Huh, I wonder if one of them is... 6-9?

06:19.846 --> 06:21.513
Pretty sure he means
69, but I'm so hungry

06:21.538 --> 06:23.155
I can't even appreciate horndog Raymond.

06:23.166 --> 06:24.672
I say we bail on the scavenger hunt.

06:24.697 --> 06:26.495
There's a restaurant one block away that

06:26.520 --> 06:28.316
