without Charles.

07:14.318 --> 07:16.284
Whoo! I'm getting married!

07:16.441 --> 07:18.787
- This is my bachelor party!
- [CHUCKLES]

07:18.822 --> 07:20.055
You guys, I can't have

07:20.090 --> 07:22.082
