stand at my wedding.

07:22.107 --> 07:23.506
I'm on the band's website.

07:23.623 --> 07:25.222
Not to tease you, but

07:25.329 --> 07:27.767
just so we all have the
complete information.

07:28.065 --> 07:30.082
- Which one is he?
- Constantine Kane.

07:30.144 --> 07:31.175
Yes.

07:32.230 --> 07:33.301
I see.

07:33.337 --> 07:34.769
Why don't you just cancel the band?

07:34.805 --> 07:36.204
If I cancel, I'll have to

07:36.240 --> 07:38.364
