bachelorettes having your back.

07:50.187 --> 07:51.562
But I wanted tonight to be fun.

07:51.608 --> 07:54.156
And it will be. We're
having a drunken adventure!

07:54.191 --> 07:55.257
Really?

07:55.292 --> 07:56.691
<i>♪ ♪</i>

07:56.727 --> 07:58.560
Okay. Yeah. Let's do it.

07:58.595 --> 08:00.695
