08:02.921 --> 08:05.088
Sorry, I have to direct it somewhere.

08:05.202 --> 08:06.581
Nice to meet you, by the way.

08:06.606 --> 08:07.893
Hey guys, if you're running out,

08:07.918 --> 08:09.649
I'm just gonna take
Hitchcock to the hospital.

08:09.673 --> 08:10.688
Is he okay?

08:10.713 --> 08:12.182
He drank a lot during
"Never Have I Ever."

08:12.206 --> 08:13.675
