08:13.710 --> 08:15.340
try to get ahead of this thing.

08:15.756 --> 08:17.122
<i>That meat was good.</i>

08:17.147 --> 08:18.613
You know what we should order?

08:18.649 --> 08:19.814
More meat.

08:19.850 --> 08:21.183
Yeah, we should.

08:21.218 --> 08:22.317
We're "The Steak Studs!"

08:22.352 --> 08:24.052
The Steak Studs!

08:24.087 --> 08:25.220
No-no-no... wait!

08:25.255 --> 08:27.022
Charles already gave us a name.

08:27.057 --> 08:29.191
And that is the only
one we're gonna use.

08:29.226 --> 08:31.126
[TOGETHER] Steak Studs! Steak Studs!

08:31.161 --> 08:32.861
