08:32.895 --> 08:34.162
- Wait-wait.
- Steak Studs...

08:34.198 --> 08:35.513
- It's Charles.
- Oh, no. Oh, no.

08:35.538 --> 08:36.575
What do we do? What do we do?

08:36.599 --> 08:37.666
Everyone, calm down.

08:37.701 --> 08:38.900
