then you stopped talking.

08:44.160 --> 08:45.907
Oh, my goodness. I'm very intoxicated.

08:45.943 --> 08:48.089
Oh, he's FaceTiming me,
you guys. What do I do?

08:48.114 --> 08:50.757
He can't know we're at the restaurant.
I need a neutral background.

08:50.781 --> 08:51.813
I'm a neutral background!

08:51.848 --> 08:53.682
- I'm huge!
- Yes. Genius.

08:54.092 --> 08:56.115
Let me put on my jacket. Okay.

08:56.553 --> 08:57.886
[CHUCKLES] Hey, best man.

08:57.921 --> 08:59.921
<i>- Jake!
- Oh, I'm so scared.</i>

08:59.957 --> 09:01.915
<i>The kidnappers have me tied up and...</i>

09:02.744 --> 09:04.259
<i>W... where are you guys?</i>

09:04.294 --> 09:06.595
I don't want to say,
in case the kidnappers are listening.

09:06.630 --> 09:08.378
<i>- Smart.
- But please hurry.</i>

09:08.417 --> 09:10.732
<i>They're torturing me like James Bond in
